Pegasus Gold Inc saidmilling operations have started at its Montana Tunnels open-pitgold, silver, zinc and lead mine near Helena.    The start-up is three months ahead of schedule and six mlndlrs under budget, the company said. Original capital cost ofthe mine was 57.5 mln dlrs, but came in at 51.5 mln dlrs, thecompany said.    After a start-up period, the mill is expected to produce 106,000 ounces of gold, 1,700,000 ounces of silver, 26,000 tonsof zinc and 5,700 tons of lead on an annual basis from4,300,000 tons of ore, the company said. Reuter&#3;